name: SIN ESPACIO
description: A collaboration with the textile workshop "Cocijo"(in honor to the lightning deity of the pre-Columbian Zapotec civilization of southern Mexico.) in San Pablo de Mitla so we involve in each other process and they show me the culture around and the archeological area and feel very sad and uncomfortable to see how this ugly "modern houses" were invading this beautiful building, we use to think on the technology in the past is not hi-tec but walking through ancient Mexico it feels more like a post-apocalyptic world lol, like in between Star Wars and Elysium.
